    <ITEM><BLIST><TITLE>File system performance</TITLE>
      <ITEM><ARTICLE><X><T>Looking for Mr. Good Block</T><A>http://sunsite.uakom.sk/sunworldonline/asm-05-1994/asm-05-sysadmin.html</A><L>en</L><F>HTML</F></X><AUTHOR><FIRSTNAME>Hal</FIRSTNAME><LASTNAME>Stern</LASTNAME></AUTHOR><DATE><YEAR>1994</YEAR><MONTH>5</MONTH></DATE><COMMENT>Hal gives some simple ideas to analyze file system accesses and to improve their performance.</COMMENT></ARTICLE></ITEM>
